snippet.textDisplay: If it's any consolation I had an Hydrocelectomy too although I was very young when I had the surgery. The aftermath was hell. It hurt to piss and if I pushed whilst doing a number 2 it felt like my balls would explode. I must of sat on the toilet for HOURS! 😂 But made a full and healthy recovery. Then later in life, around 5 or 6 years ago I got an infection in my Epididymis. Luckily caught it early and a course of antibiotics got rid of it. I don't know HOW you managed to put up with the pain because it felt like everytime I took a step, it felt like I was getting kicked in the nuts! Anyways man, best thing to do is take it easy, rest up and you'll make a full recovery in no time. Sorry for the long-winded comment.👍
